# Understanding TypeScript

TypeScript adds static typing to JavaScript, making it more robust and maintainable.

## Benefits

- Type safety
- Better IDE support
- Enhanced refactoring
- Clearer code documentation

## Basic Types

```typescript
let name: string = 'John';
let age: number = 30;
let isActive: boolean = true;
```

## Interfaces

```typescript
interface User {
  name: string;
  age: number;
}
```
